{"id": 7146, "title": "Ticket #7146: Improve condor_annex's Spot Fleet documentation", "description": "<blockquote>\nTo construct an annex using a Spot Fleet, you must select the instance profile.  This is <a class=\"external\" href=\"http://htcondor.readthedocs.io/en/latest/cloud-computing/annex-users-guide.html\">documented</a>, but it does not mention security groups (at least one is required) or key pair names (which may also be important).\n\n<p>The documentation should be updated to include them for the 8.8 series; that section should be removed from the v8.9 manual when <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"active\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=7089\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7089'); return false;\" title=\"condor_annex -aws-spot-fleet UX missing defaults\">#7089</a></span> is done.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Jul-10 17:01</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/73590553f5fe1b5b2a227e0dc8c14ff83def597b\">[57379]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=7146\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7146'); return false;\" title=\"Improve condor_annex's Spot Fleet documentation\">#7146</a></span>) Stable branch documentation update.  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Jul-10 16:53</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/b77c